{"tid":1038301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海邊驚現乳白海洋！竟是公鲱魚大爆射","createTime":"2019-02-26T14:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T15:42:36.000Z","uid":150609,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"58788bb6fc83e119dec07e2a7116b30df425094f","tid":1038301,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:42:10.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n日本北海道小樽市近日出現自然奇觀，一大群公鯡魚為了讓母鯡魚成功繁殖下一代，在沿岸大量射精，且精液還將附近海域變成「乳白色的海洋」，這個奇景在小樽近海500公尺擴散。專家表示，這種乳白色大海的現象，在當地被叫做「群來」，據說看到的人會得到好運。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QW73QHV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQW73QHV.jpg&h=eaafeba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合日本媒體報導，2月20日北海道小樽市張碓町一路往船濱町沿岸出現大量鯡魚群聚集，長達數公里的海岸都遭到公鲱魚的精液染色，變成乳白色的海水。據當地研究機構指稱，鲱魚群每年都會在北海道附近進行繁殖，而這是2019年第一次出現，相較去年足足晚了20天。此外，小樽市北部的鹽谷沿岸，於同一天也出現類似的景觀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cRDq32W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcRDq32W.jpg&h=1cfdb61c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小樽市綜合博物館的專家指出，鯡魚在1945年左右於北海道消失，但近幾年又大量出現，而公鲱魚集體排精的現象在當地被稱為「（群来，くき）」，由於在前幾年想看到是很困難的，所以當地又盛傳「看到群來會帶來幸運」的傳說。小樽市漁會也表示，鯡魚捕撈已在上個月10日解禁，當地到3月25日都會對鲱魚進行漁撈作業，也歡迎大家前來享用鲱魚美食。（編輯：于川）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XTN3QJh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXTN3QJh.gif&h=97b32bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/26/224129_7d2be911bd655d29cc5654f77b160018.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F26%2F224129_7d2be911bd655d29cc5654f77b160018.gif&h=9a66305e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2cp2mQb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2cp2mQb.gif&h=425f0d03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a27e1d5d17f3ce70168b87a9c26fe852f70e84c","tid":1038301,"uid":7206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cx7jo56.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCx7jo56.gif&h=3461d9fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fe9363665e4c5135e8f828a9e0e458b58406237","tid":1038301,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:49:56.000Z","msg":"想落去游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b605a2703d6658d1983fb23c496324d09e9e0100","tid":1038301,"uid":56698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:00:24.000Z","msg":"諗起啲濕鳩日本AV射精射成3分鐘 水浸咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55a2c7bbabec55d0dee66bc55c4358a7dedcd97","tid":1038301,"uid":80072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"鲱你老母"},{"pid":"a1f06e106234129258ac4b0cf55f0f33b84f09b5","tid":1038301,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a55a2c7bbabec55d0dee66bc55c4358a7dedcd97","tid":1038301,"uid":80072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"鲱你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:42:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B5%B7%E9%82%8A%E9%A9%9A%E7%8F%BE%E4%B9%B3%E7%99%BD%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B-%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%85%AC%E9%B2%B1%E9%AD%9A%E5%A4%A7%E7%88%86%E5%B0%84-121531740.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2582%258A%25E9%25A9%259A%25E7%258F%25BE%25E4%25B9%25B3%25E7%2599%25BD%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25B4%258B-%25E7%25AB%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%25B2%25B1%25E9%25AD%259A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%25B0%2584-121531740.html&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6V8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=763d5d63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B5%